NG0748:1: dgu rtse'i nang nas 'dir shog la //
NG0748:2: dgra la gri 'thab yams su phob //
NG0748:3: badzra ne lam ma rag badzra ni pa li badzra /
NG0748:5: shar lho rin chen thang dkyil nas //
NG0748:6: ging chen rdo rje legs pa khyod //
NG0748:7: dgra la pho log gzer thabs thong *//
NG0748:8: srid pa'i dregs pa chen po khyod //
NG0748:9: phyag na rdo rje bka' byung gis //
NG0748:10: badzra ni la dun trag rag badzra lam pa rag sha ma badzra /
NG0748:11: rang rang las kyi skal long la //
NG0748:12: bcol ba myur du grub par gyis //
NG0748:13: las la mngag cing bskul bar bshad //
NG0748:14: dug gi spu gri gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0748:15: las mngag pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0748:16: / de nas bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag pos //
NG0748:17: 'dus pa'i tshogs de dag la rgyud gtad pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0748:18: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NG0748:19: khro bo rngam pa rol pa'i tshogs //
NG0748:20: 'jig rten dregs pa rnams kyi tshogs //
NG0748:21: ma mo mkha' 'gro gdug pa'i tshogs //
NG0748:22: gtsang ris mgon po lha yi tshogs //
NG0748:23: rgyal po sde bzhi 'khor dang bcas //
NG0748:24: sha za rngam 'jigs srog len tshogs //
NG0748:26: bka' yi gsang rgyud spu gri 'di //
NG0748:27: bstan pa rin chen gter gyi mchog / drag sngags
NG0748:28: dgu thog sbab chen dug / me dbal spu gri
NG0748:29: mtshon cha dbal // dug gi spu gri gsang rgyud 'di //
NG0748:30: don gyi ngo bo ma nor gtad //
NG0748:31: dug chen bya bar gang gsung ba //
NG0748:32: drag sngags dbal gyi nus pa yis //
NG0748:33: log pa'i blo can phung byed pa'o //
NG0748:34: spu gri zhes bya gang gsungs pa //
NG0748:35: drag po so yi ngar mchog gis //
NG0748:36: gang yang gdug med myur du gcod //
NG0748:37: gsang ba zhes su gang gsungs pa //
NG0748:39: blo dman rmongs pas rtogs pa dka' //
NG0748:40: spyad na rang nyid phur bar 'gyur //
NG0748:41: rgyud ces bya bar gang gsungs pa //
NG0748:42: lha dang sngags bdag ting 'dzin dang *//
NG0748:43: dam rdzas mchod pa rgyan dang gnas //
NG0748:44: lta ba dam tshig dbang gsum dang *//
NG0748:45: bsnyen bsgrub sngags kyi rim pa dang *//
NG0748:46: mu la big nan phag thum ril khril ya dbang po thum ril tham /
NG0748:47: thun dang 'khor lo ling ga dang *//
NG0748:48: dmod pa gdab pa'i drag sngags dang *//
NG0748:49: las kyi rim pa ma lus kun //
NG0748:51: de phyir mtshan gyi nges tshig ldan //
NG0748:52: don 'di ma nor khyed la gtad //
NG0748:53: rig pa sems kyi rtsal gyis long *//
NG0748:54: chags pa chen po'i brda yis bzung *//
NG0748:55: snying la gab cing sba bar gyis //
NG0748:56: e ma gsang ba'i rgyud 'di yang *//
NG0748:57: brnag pa las thabs drag po rnams //
NG0748:59: kun gyi thun mong ma yin gsang *//
NG0748:60: nus pa dpag med brjod las 'das //
NG0748:61: de phyir gsang rgyud spu gri 'di //
NG0748:62: dmod pa las kyi 'bru rgod rnams //
NG0748:63: nga yi thugs kyi klong nas byung *//
NG0748:65: phyi rabs rnal 'byor rigs chen rnams //
NG0748:67: gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje can //
NG0748:68: gsad bsrung dbab gcad don bzhi rdzogs //
NG0748:69: nga yi thugs kyi sras su dgongs //
NG0748:71: sras dang spun bsgom byin gyis brlob //
NG0748:72: sngags bdag nyid kying bsrung zhing 'khur //
NG0748:75: blo dman bgrod med rmongs la med //
NG0748:76: mi mos smad pa'i skyon rnams kyang *//
NG0748:77: gsang bdag ngas kyang brjod du med //
NG0748:78: thabs rnams ldan dang mi ldan pas //
NG0748:79: rtsibs la spu gri tshan re gnas //
NG0748:81: de phyir yun ring gter du 'gyur //
NG0748:83: yun du bsgrubs na slu ba med //
NG0748:84: drag sngags rnol dbal gang chen rnams //
NG0748:85: ra chod byas na rang gcod brlag / bag dang ldan zhing nyid las bgros //
NG0748:86: 'di bshad dgu thog rbab chen bzhin //
NG0748:87: gang la phog kyang 'joms par byed //
NG0748:88: glu ba med pa'i las yin te //
NG0748:89: gzu lum ra chod phung ba'i rgyu //
NG0748:90: bka' gsang thob na ren chen gter //
NG0748:91: me lce mtshon cha dgu thogs kyis //
NG0748:92: lta de drod ldan mtshon cha'i mchog / 'di byung
NG0748:93: dus na bstan pa 'jig / de tshe sngags rgod
NG0748:94: nus pa 'byung *// gang la rgyab kyang 'chor mi srid //
NG0748:95: sgrol ging rdo rje nag po yis //
NG0748:96: mthar thug gnad kyi gsang rgyud yin //
NG0748:97: nus pa rang dbang med par 'byung *//
NG0748:98: gang brtsams las la thogs med 'grub //
NG0748:99: dam tshig ldan zhing lta ba rtogs //
NG0748:100: gri thod zhabs ma re bas dril //
NG0748:101: dbang bgrod sdig pa'i phyogs tsam spang *//
NG0748:102: mchog tu slob dpon mnyes pa gces //
NG0748:103: dmod pa'i drag sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0748:104: de ldan nus pa thogs med do //
NG0748:105: gsang rgyud dug gi spu grir bshad //
NG0748:106: de nas gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje snying pos
NG0748:107: gsungs pa la thams cad yi rangs te mngon par
NG0748:108: bstod do // dug gi spu gri gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0748:109: gtad cing gdams pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NG0748:110: // dpal mgon po nag po dug gi spu gri
